            "title": "李強在紐約會見「友好團體」：中美可以也應當成為夥伴和朋友",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"李強在紐約會見「友好團體」：中美可以也應當成為夥伴和朋友\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"768\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cPGvK99MKx6PNGgDIwCWXg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc2ODtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/9ace5b90-9a7d-11f0-bb75-90d2bd23ea88\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">李強在紐約會見「友好團體」：中美可以也應當成為夥伴和朋友</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
